characterDescription: The Black Fisher is an entity of unknown origin and/or occupation who is referred to by a darkeyed street juggler in a death rattle:

characterDetails.Notes:
Whether Dai-gonarthis and the Black Fisher are one in the same, or separate entities, remains unknown.
A mad beggar, Ahu, asks Dalinar which one got him, naming the Black Fisher with other Unmade (i.e., the Spawning Mother, the Faceless, and Moelach.)
